│ ## Initial Observations ##                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ The reproducer is already minimized. Based on my experience in debugging these bugs, the issue is likely introduced by the *first transformation*, or due to incorrect analysis information feeding into it.   │
│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass regardless of whether it's in the `vector-combine` module or other modules.                           │
│ #### Opt Information ####                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ To gather more insight, I ran `opt` to inspect both the transformations and the analysis results. Below are the command and the resulting log:                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                                        │
│ $ bin/opt --passes=vector-combine -S -mtriple=x86_64-- -mattr=SSE2 --debug-only=vector-combine /tmp/reprod_mom2f126.ll                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│                                                                                                                                                                                                                │
│ VECTORCOMBINE on instsimplify_folder_crash                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ VC: Visiting:   %shuffle.1 = shufflevector <4 x i64> %in, <4 x i64> zeroinitializer, <4 x i32> <i32 4, i32 5, i32 2, i32 3>                                                                                    │
│ VC: Visiting:   %e.0 = extractelement <4 x i64> zeroinitializer, i64 0                                                                                                                                         │
│ VC: Visiting:   %e.1 = extractelement <4 x i64> %shuffle.1, i64 1                                                                                                                                              │
│ VC: Visiting:   %shift = shufflevector <4 x i64> %shuffle.1, <4 x i64> poison, <4 x i32> <i32 1, i32 poison, i32 poison, i32 poison>                                                                           │
│ Found a shuffle feeding two shuffles:   %shift = shufflevector <4 x i64> %shuffle.1, <4 x i64> poison, <4 x i32> <i32 1, i32 poison, i32 poison, i32 poison>                                                   │
│   OldCost: 2 vs NewCost: 1                                                                                                                                                                                     │
│ VC: Replacing:   %shift = shufflevector <4 x i64> %shuffle.1, <4 x i64> poison, <4 x i32> <i32 1, i32 poison, i32 poison, i32 poison>                                                                          │
│          With: <4 x i64> <i64 0, i64 undef, i64 undef, i64 undef>                                                                                                                                              │
